description: Amazing city views from this prime location, second floor unit boasting oversized windows, two decorative fireplaces in the open concept living space including living/dining/kitchen plus in-unit laundry, oversized closets and full bath.  Primary bedroom has a walk-in closet and bedroom two offers access to the oversized deck with room for furniture, bikes and other outdoor storage.  Gorgeous skyline sunset views, minutes to the beach.  Bus stop right outside the door; close to downtown, highways and all that Southie has to offer!
